abstract: Israeli authorities report police officers have wounded Palestinian man for allegedly stabbing and seriously injuring Israeli man in northern city of Netanya; also say police have arrested another Palestinian man for stabbing several people in Rishon Lezion, Israel.
lead_paragraph: A Palestinian man wounded an Israeli man in the city of Netanya on Monday, the police said, and another Palestinian stabbed several people near Tel Aviv.

headline.main: Israel: Stabbing Attacks Move Beyond Jerusalem and West Bank
headline.print_headline: Middle East; Israel: Stabbing Attacks Move Beyond Jerusalem and West Bank
